message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite both the article (preferred-citation) and this record."
title: "m6AAtlas: Pan-cancer alteration landscape of the m6A epitranscriptome machinery"
abstract: "Curated copy-number-alteration and somatic-mutation frequency tables for 17 m6A epitranscriptome machinery genes across 32 TCGA PanCancer Atlas tumour types (n = 10,195), with a reproducible Python retrieval pipeline and an R figure-generation script."
type: dataset
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-06-12"
